strings: <voice_0x01000ECD><se_def>Prince Charmles: You feather-brained rascal! You forgot to use the lizard humour I gave you, didn't you!?
<voice_0x01000ECE><se_def>Prince Charmles: Didn't I tell you that you wouldn't be able to get close to a lizard without it? Now do as you're told and stop wasting my time!
